OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FThe heatwave continues on
OL,6,FSaturday with another dry and sunny
OL,7,Fday. Feeling hot with high UV but
OL,8,Fperhaps a more notable breeze
OL,9,Fdeveloping later in the day.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStaying
OL,12,Fdry and settled throughout Sunday and
OL,13,Fearly next week with plenty of
OL,14,Fsunshine. Remaining very warm although
OL,15,Fan easterly breeze will bring a little
OL,16,Frelief to the hot conditions.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
